name: QWeather Icon
description:
和风天气图标 QWeather Icons


QWeather Icons&&Fonts are open source, beautiful weather icons and iconfonts for QWeather API/SDK and can be used in any other projects.


You can download and install QWeather Icons in several ways:

  • npm install: npm i qweather-icons
  • Download packaged files

For more installation info (e.g. jsDelivr), see Docs:Install.


https://dev.qweather.com/docs/start/icons/

https://github.com/qwd/Icons#qweather-icons
